H2K_futex_init
--------------

.. cfunction:: void H2K_futex_init(void)

Description
~~~~~~~~~~~

:cfunc:`H2K_futex_init()` initializes the futex data structures.

Functionality
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

H2K_futexhash is set to NULL for each element in the array.

